metadata.description:
Black Dave is feeling good. It’s really that simple. Taking up space and creating, the nonconformist musician, producer, rapper, visual artist, anime and streetwear enthusiast, and web3 innovator unapologetically thinks outside the box. He’d rather break them all open.

Here's how Black Dave describes “Feel Good,” his latest track:

"Sometimes you gotta remind the world that you’re the one not the two. 'Feel Good' is my reminder to y’all."

----

This is the second track from HIGH FREQUENCY Volume 1 — a compilation album curated by NOISE. 

Read our interview with Black Dave here: https://noisedao.mirror.xyz/b2ByTlc78Jns3YtgW3WB37O_hm-_XoueitXxlu34U_c
